Cyber Claw:




"Wait?" Cyber Claw said, repeating Zardus' last words to her. She lowered 
herself closer to the ground to the Alliance member. "I wait for no bot." 
She was ready to charge at him. Getting her weapons was on her mind. Grab 
this slag of a Predacon, get some answers out of him and get him to take her 
to Megatron himself.
